<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٨٤١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5093">أَبُو نُعَيْمٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4042">عَبْدِ الْمَلِكِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3745">أَبِي سَلَمَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي</a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هُرَيْرَةَ <span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«أَصْدَقُ كَلِمَةٍ قَالَهَا الشَّاعِرُ،<span class="c5"> كَلِمَةُ لَبِيدٍ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أَلَا كُلُّ شَيْءٍ مَا خَلَا اللهَ بَاطِلٌ،<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَكَادَ أُمَيَّةُ بْنُ أَبِي الصَّلْتِ أَنْ يُسْلِمَ.»<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>